Unfortunately time does not allow us to help with individual problems
unless a serious bug arises in any of the code. Please persevere, look
at our own tracks, and talk to other people about any problems or
good ideas. Feel free to write to us with your comments however.


@{U}The BBS@{UU}


The Silltunna BBS is available for any XTR news and all the latest
tracks. When you have done @{B}and fully tested@{UB} a track then please
call our BBS and upload it there before anywhere else if possible, or
UUEncode it and mail it to rich@xtreme.demon.co.uk with the subject clearly
marked "UUE : XTR Track". Also upload any tracks onto any Aminet site and
place them on any Public Domain/Magazine Coverdiscs. No profit may
be made from the selling of any XTreme Racing related material without
our prior consent. Only Custom XTreme Racing Tracks and Custom
XTreme Racing Graphics may be placed on Magazine Coverdiscs or in the
public domain without our prior consent. See the Disclaimer.

